0_Sprinkle 1_yeast 2_and 3_sugar 4_over 5_warm 6_water. 

7_Keep 8_aside 9_for 10_5 11_minutes 12_or 13_till 14_frothy. 

15_Mix 16_salt 17_and 18_flour, 19_take 20_in 21_a 22_large 23_plate. 

24_Make 25_well 26_in 27_centre. 28_Put 29_curds 30_in 31_well. 

32_Sprinkle 33_baking 34_powder 35_over 36_curds. 

37_Allow 38_to 39_stand 40_for 41_2-3 42_minutes. 

43_Pour 44_oil, 45_yeast 46_solution, 47_in 48_well 49_and 50_mix 51_gradually. 

52_Use 53_milk 54_as 55_required, 56_to 57_make 58_a 59_soft 60_stiff 61_dough. 

62_Brush 63_dough 64_will 65_oil. 66_Cover 67_with 68_inverted 69_bowl. 

70_Keep 71_aside 72_for 73_4 74_hours. 75_Longer 76_if 77_weather 78_is 79_cold. 

80_Grease 81_palms 82_well 83_and 84_punch 85_dough 86_till 87_soft 88_and 89_elastic. 

90_Cover 91_again 92_and 93_keep 94_aside 95_for 96_10 97_minutes. 

98_Break 99_of 100_a 101_lump 102_of 103_dough. 

104_Roll 105_or 106_pat 107_to 108_a 109_thick 110_round 111_about 112_6" 113_diam. 

114_Roast 115_on 116_hot 117_griddle, 118_or 119_tandoor, 120_till 121_golden 122_spots 123_appear. 

124_Or 125_shallow 126_fry 127_on 128_griddle. 

129_Serve 130_hot 131_with 132_gravied 133_vegetables, 134_dals, 135_etc. 
